#

Борщ (Beetroot Soup)

60 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

UkrainianEastern European

Course:

Main CourseSoup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A hearty and vibrant soup made with beets, vegetables, and a hint of sour cream, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrot: 1 large, grated
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • sour cream: for serving (optional)
  • fresh dill: for garnish (optional)
